  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1175770/extras/63ace02c06616ecdfe944a6d902bbe3e.avif?t=1756860477\" width=616 height=180 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><i><strong>Easy to pick up and play, with infinite depth to master.</strong></i></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>TopplePOP</strong> is physics puzzle action!  1-4 players guide bendy animal acrobats on rubber bands in a race to rescue their pals.  Various game modes for spectacular couch co-op parties, solo speedruns, eSports tournaments and weekly challenge leaderboards.  Style your unique bungee blockbuster and <i><strong>become champions!  Or not</strong>!  </i>And chill exploring an infinite variety of zen puzzles.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>- <i>100% </i>💖<i>Steam Deck Compatible! -</i></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">Take your puzzle gaming <i><strong>\"off the grid\"</strong> for fast & fluid freestyle physics fun!</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 1 - 4 Players</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use Keys, Keys + Mouse or Controller (recommended)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Solo / Co-op Story Campaign</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >PvE against AI opponents</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >local multiplayer,  online multiplayer  or  both at once!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Casual Parties and Spectacular eSports Tournaments!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >PvP - 1v1,  2v2 Teams,  3 to 4 Player free-for-all.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Daily & Weekly Leaderboard Challenges</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>( * local multiplayer requires at least 1 controller )</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1175770/extras/017df9995c0189419b4f707b23c30fc1.poster.avif?t=1756860477\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1175770/extras/017df9995c0189419b4f707b23c30fc1.webm?t=1756860477\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><i><strong>  </strong></i></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1175770/extras/9ae5ffe136984d29184a3ea9dfdb26cf.avif?t=1756860477\" width=616 height=75 /></span><i><strong><strong><i>Guide bendy animal acrobats on rubber bands with gamepads (recommended) or keyboard / keys & mouse.</i></strong></strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1175770/extras/64a33b1c48bdb6e83feeed6c091036fd.poster.avif?t=1756860477\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1175770/extras/64a33b1c48bdb6e83feeed6c091036fd.webm?t=1756860477\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1175770/extras/c129671fb2c9c88aa64402f94558b56e.avif?t=1756860477\" width=616 height=75 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><i><strong><strong><i>Swing, fling, rotate, shove, stack and topple colorful blocks! Connect 4 to combo and POP! Chain combos to topple your opponents!</i></strong></strong></i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1175770/extras/34227324e461d17a44624cf14c9749ab.poster.avif?t=1756860477\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1175770/extras/34227324e461d17a44624cf14c9749ab.webm?t=1756860477\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1175770/extras/e8a673f109055eda8e26ad30403abfab.avif?t=1756860477\" width=616 height=75 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><i><strong>Your pals are trapped, transformed into Grumble blocks!  Rescue new team members and learn their skills! </strong></i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1175770/extras/2b0a3ec91ab677cc06c2956e4bc404cf.poster.avif?t=1756860477\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1175770/extras/2b0a3ec91ab677cc06c2956e4bc404cf.webm?t=1756860477\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1175770/extras/13828f0f4867fd9588d8401e9d9fca7f.avif?t=1756860477\" width=616 height=75 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><i><strong><strong>